<span id="freeTextContainer14196984337064855727">Civil war novel that was so so descriptive with multiple storylines of plantations,slaves, soldiers in battles,abolitionists, war widows trying to survive and all the politics in this sad time of our history....tough to read in many parts, compelling, sad and horrific and yet it ends in hope.</span>

