      <span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_review_1442914523'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it gr-button gr-button--small" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F290260.Jacob_s_Ladder">Like</a></span>
